@ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5271

### health check
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/health


### Get all users
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/users

### Create user
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890"
}

### User authentication
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/users/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### Get user based on ID
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/users/{{userId}}

### ===== ProductService 通过网关 =====

